rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0001
rows.name:
I really hope we'll be able to join
up with Kasumi soon.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0002
rows.name: It isn't far to Felt now.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0003
rows.name:
In fact, we should be there in no time
as long as we stick to the path.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0004
rows.name:
I wonder what Kasumi will think of
Satahiko when they meet?

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0005
rows.name: It'll be interesting, that's for sure.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0007
rows.name:
Don't worry, Satahiko.
Kasumi is one of the loveliest people
I've met.
